snippet.title: Help Bipboop - Wishlist Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Help Bipboop : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1948300/Help_Bipboop/

Help Bipboop is a puzzle game where you place blocks to create a path related to the movements of Bipboop. Many blocks, many path, many levels. Can you help bipboop to reach the end of his journey ?

Go wishlist Help Bipboop to help us in our development !

Twitter / X : https://twitter.com/unimolix
